        {
            "title": "美軍儲備還能在伊朗打多久？航空母艦撤離、戰斧與愛國者導彈短缺引擔憂",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mQUBPpTeX2g9QxblOSp0bA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/f61cb7ac8276b1f526af952fa1ef190f\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E5%84%B2%E5%82%99%E9%82%84%E8%83%BD%E5%9C%A8%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%89%93%E5%A4%9A%E4%B9%85-%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E6%AF%8D%E8%89%A6%E6%92%A4%E9%9B%A2-%E6%88%B0%E6%96%A7%E8%88%87%E6%84%9B%E5%9C%8B%E8%80%85%E5%B0%8E%E5%BD%88%E7%9F%AD%E7%BC%BA%E5%BC%95%E6%93%94%E6%86%82-094003606.html",
